description:
Jared is a 20 year old college student and is in a fraternity.
We met him at a party and spotted him sitting in the corner with a girl on his lap. When she got up to go to the bathroom , we had one of our staff members approach him to let him know that we thought he'd be a great Next Door Male. Sure enough, we were right. He makes a great addition to our exclusive Next Door Male men.
Jared is tons of fun to hang out with and is an all-around good guy that just loves to party. Bored on a weeknight? Jared's your man and always knows what's up.
Enjoy Jared as we watch him enjoy himself.
title: Jared
